properties.areaDesc: Eastern Norton Sound and Nulato Hills
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 18 at 6:14AM AKST until February 19 at 6:00AM AKST by NWS Fairbanks, AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow and blowing snow occurring. Plan on difficult travel
conditions. Additional snow accumulations of 3 inches are
expected. Visibility may be reduced to one half mile or less at
times.

* WHERE...Eastern Norton Sound and Nulato Hills.

* WHEN...Until 6 AM Wednesday.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Winds gusting to 40 mph will cause areas
of blowing and drifting snow.
properties.instruction:
A Winter Weather Advisory for snow and blowing snow means periods
of snow and blowing snow will cause travel difficulties.
